CodeIgniter /application folder.

Postup na instalaciu(Ubuntu):
1. Chod na tuto stranku a klikni fork: https://github.com/RegioPlanet/regioplanet-codeigniter
2. cd /var/www
3. git init
4. git clone git@github.com:tvojusername/regioplanet-codeigniter.git
5. cd regioplanet-codeigniter/
6. git remote add upstream git@github.com:tvojusername/regioplanet-codeigniter.git
7. zlozka application/ by mala byt na mieste :)
8. stiahni: CodeIgniter_2.1.0.zip
9. rozbal vsetky adresare a subory OKREM application/ (system,user_guide,index.php,license.txt) 
do /var/www/regioplanet-codeigniter/
10. http://localhost/regioplanet-codeigniter/

Kto pracoval s CodeIgniterom, si to vie nastavit aj sam :) 
Potom odporucam zmenit nastavenia na DB a ostatne default nastavenia.



